title: Denzel Ward's Texans Hold off Jarvis Landry's Browns in Madden 20 Tournament
description: Denzel Ward and the Houston Texans defeated  Jarvis Landry  and the Cleveland Browns 10-9 Wednesday in The Checkdown and Madden 20's tournament for COVID-19 relief efforts...
